  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.6">
<l>niṉṟaṉa riruntaṉar kiṭantaṉar tirintaṉar</l>
<l>niṉṟila riruntilar kiṭantilar tirintila</l>
<l>reṉṟumō riyalviṉar eṉaniṉai variyava</l>
<l>reṉṟumō riyalvoṭu niṉṟaven tiṭarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He stood, sat, lay, wandered,</l>
<l>he did not stand, sit, lay, wander –</l>
<l>he who is difficult to think as one with one nature always,</l>
<l>he is our firm point who remains with one nature always.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
